        <h1 class="mb-3">How to Make Your Digital Art Look More Natural</h1>
        <div class="podcast-title">Thoughts on Illustration</div>
        <div class="text-muted mb-4">April 28 at 7:00 AM</div>

        <audio controls class="audio-player" data-guid="012175d7-87b2-484b-a843-d0f8dcad32f6">
